value.title: Price / Shipping / Fee..
value.usage:
These values have to be numbers and use only one decimal point, 1.500 will be interpreted as 1.5
example: 150.10

currency.title: Currency
currency.usage:
Use only the allowed currency
example: â‚¬

address.title: Shipping / Billing address
address.usage: Keep the address in the format of the field placeholder, if you see 4 lines use 4 lines

name.title: Name
name.usage:
Your name, at least a first name and a last name separated by a space
example: Rob Banks

email.title: Email
email.usage: Something went wrong while sending your email please contact support

date1.title: Date
date1.usage:
In the format of M/D/YYYY, it will be converted depending on the brand
example: 9/11/2001

apple_url.title: Url
apple_url.usage:
You entered a wrong url make sure to press buy before copying and use US apple.com
example: https://www.apple.com/shop/buy-airpods/airpods-max/space-gray

unknown.title: Unknown
unknown.usage: Wow you caught a very rare error message us to get it resolved

image_url.title: Direct image link
image_url.usage:
Make sure the image link works when you put it in your browser, also make sure it is a direct image link
you can use this to create your own https://postimages.org/

stockx_order_status.title: StockX Order Status
stockx_order_status.usage: Make sure that the status is delivered, ordered or verified

stockx_url.title: Url
stockx_url.usage:
You entered a wrong url make sure to use a valid url from stockx.com by putting it in your browser, the url has to have a product
example: https://stockx.com/adidas-predator-elite-ft-fg-vivid-horizon

condition.title: Condition
condition.usage:
